title: CivRealms Beers
author: axusgrad
pages:
#- §6§lBeers of CivRealms§0
§0
§0      (1st Edition)§0
§0
§0There is no wider variety of drinks to be made from one or two ingredients than Beer.  From a quick Pale Ale to a rich Doppel-bock, there is a beer for every occasion.
#- 
§0      §0§nBeer Tips§0
§0
§0Beer requires Hops.  World-wide availability is still limited, but you should be able to find it at fine grocers such as Diligent Supplying.§0

#-   §0§nBeer Tips (cont.)§0
§0
§0Check the cauldron with a gold clock for exact timing; the type of beer you get depends on it!§0
§0
§0Barrel aging ruins beer very quickly.  Once you bottle the beer, it is ready for sale or consumption!
#-   §0§nBeer Tips (cont.)§0
§0
§0This first edition has 8 beers, but there may be more undiscovered! Try adding a third ingredient, and see what happens.
