#- Wow, what a variety of beer, from just wheat and hops!§0
§0
§0This author has yet to try adding sugar, apples, or other ingredients to beer, and looks forward to future research.
#- CivRealms is unique among the worlds, for using custom ingredients such as hops.§0
§0
§0For an alternative to beer, check out §1§lLiquors of Civrealms
#- 